          <details class="ff-disc ff-disc--premium ff-faq__item" data-ff-faq-item>
            <summary class="ff-disc__sum" aria-controls="faqAnonBody">
              <span class="ff-disc__meta" id="faqAnonTitle">
                <span class="ff-kicker">Can I donate anonymously?</span><br />
                <span class="ff-help">Yes — toggle “anonymous”</span>
              </span>
              <span class="ff-pill" aria-hidden="true">Open</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="ff-disc__body" id="faqAnonBody" role="region" aria-labelledby="faqAnonTitle">
              <ul class="ff-bul">
                <li>Check “Donate anonymously” to hide your name from public lists.</li>
                <li>Your receipt still arrives by email.</li>
                <li>You can switch recognition preferences anytime before submitting.</li>
              </ul>
              <p class="ff-help ff-muted ff-mt-2">
                Tip: anonymous hides your name publicly, not from organizer/payment processor records.
              </p>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="ff-disc ff-disc--premium ff-faq__item" data-ff-faq-item>
            <summary class="ff-disc__sum" aria-controls="faqWhereBody">
              <span class="ff-disc__meta" id="faqWhereTitle">
                <span class="ff-kicker">Where does the money go?</span><br />
                <span class="ff-help">See Allocation in Impact</span>
              </span>
              <span class="ff-pill" aria-hidden="true">Open</span>
            </summary>
            <div class="ff-disc__body" id="faqWhereBody" role="region" aria-labelledby="faqWhereTitle">
              <ul class="ff-bul">
                <li>Gym time, tournament fees, travel support, and gear.</li>
                <li>Scholarships for families who need help.</li>
                <li>Allocation breakdown is shown and updated by organizers.</li>
              </ul>
              <div class="ff-row ff-wrap ff-mt-2" role="group" aria-label="Allocation actions">
                <a class="ff-btn ff-btn--ghost ff-btn--sm" href="#impact">View Impact</a>
                <a class="ff-btn ff-btn--ghost ff-btn--sm" href="#progress">View Progress</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </details>

          <details class="ff-disc ff-disc--premium ff-faq__item" data-ff-faq-item>
            <summary class="ff-disc__sum" aria-controls="faqRefundBody">
